In this world, how many people come for profits and

71
00:12:15,070 --> 00:12:17,270
die for profits?

72
00:12:18,420 --> 00:12:26,710
And only you will feel disgust for this kind of thing and even blame yourself.

73
00:12:26,710 --> 00:12:29,140
This isn't your fault.

74
00:12:32,620 --> 00:12:35,780
You shouldn't have to bear such pain.

75
00:12:38,560 --> 00:12:40,710
This is unfair.

76
00:12:43,500 --> 00:12:47,510
Girl, are you awake?

77
00:12:47,510 --> 00:12:49,370
