So-called justice,

90
00:13:49,920 --> 00:13:53,380
before making decisions,

91
00:13:53,380 --> 00:13:57,910
won't withstand even a single blow because of one's selfishness.

92
00:13:57,910 --> 00:14:02,670
The whole house died because of me.

93
00:14:03,800 --> 00:14:06,780
It was because of me.

94
00:14:06,780 --> 00:14:09,810
It was all because of me.

95
00:14:09,810 --> 00:14:11,530
It's okay.

96
00:14:11,530 --> 00:14:13,100
Everything is fine.

97
00:14:13,100 --> 00:14:15,170
Girl,

98
00:14:16,560 --> 00:14:19,750
we aren't afraid of mentioning it.

99
00:14:19,750 --> 00:14:22,520
Nor do we fear to bear the consequences.

100
00:14:22,520 --> 00:14:30,100
But there is no need for us to bear all these sorrows and not let go continuously.

101
00:14:30,100 --> 00:14:32,100
Okay?

102
00:14:34,470 --> 00:14:40,460
There are some things that are just like this.

103
00:14:40,460 --> 00:14:44,830
It's hard to distinguish the significant from the insignificant.

104
00:14:46,110 --> 00:14:51,910
One can only make a decision between pain and even more pain.

105
00:14:55,870 --> 00:15:01,060
I am very fortunate to have met you in this life.

106
00:15:05,840 --> 00:15:07,830
Same for me.

107
00:15:07,830 --> 00:15:10,830
It's okay. It's okay.

108
00:15:13,690 --> 00:15:18,070
I will always think that yesterday's events were a bit strange.

109
00:15:18,070 --> 00:15:23,620
Plough's royal clan is being unscrupulous in hiding a large secret.

110
00:15:25,030 --> 00:15:29,660
What really has happened in Young Phoenix Lake?

111
00:15:31,210 --> 00:15:34,640
We don't have any clue now.

112
00:15:34,640 --> 00:15:38,300
Since ancient times, Plough has been like the North Star.

113
00:15:38,300 --> 00:15:40,830
It sets the peace of the world.

114
00:15:41,860 --> 00:15:46,400
No matter what, Plough cannot succumb to chaos.

115
00:15:47,470 --> 00:15:51,480
And it is time to visit the Lord of Plough.

116
00:16:26,190 --> 00:16:30,810
In just a few days, there are already that many urgent reports?

117
00:16:30,810 --> 00:16:33,710
The state affairs of Plough have always been divided into three levels.

118
00:16:33,710 --> 00:16:37,430
Divided according to urgency and importance.

119
00:16:37,430 --> 00:16:42,750
It's already rare if there are two to three urgent reports in a day.

120
00:16:42,750 --> 00:16:47,340
But now, you did well that you have gotten me such annoyances.

121
00:16:53,590 --> 00:16:55,830
Why is there no one answering?

122
00:16:55,830 --> 00:16:59,250
Don't you all usually have many opinions?

123
00:16:59,250 --> 00:17:00,690
Well?

124
00:17:00,690 --> 00:17:03,380
Why are you sealing yourselves away in silence?

125
00:17:03,380 --> 00:17:05,000
The Queen is severely ill.

126
00:17:05,000 --> 00:17:08,550
I am to manage all state affairs on her behalf.

127
00:17:08,550 --> 00:17:11,280
Am I not qualified enough?

128
00:17:11,280 --> 00:17:14,600
Or are you dissatisfied with the Queen's decree?

129
00:17:14,600 --> 00:17:17,070
I do not dare.

130
00:17:21,660 --> 00:17:23,850
Retreat now.

131
00:17:39,790 --> 00:17:44,050
Crown Prince Wuji sent someone to deliver his visiting tally.

132
00:17:44,050 --> 00:17:46,340
Crown Prince Wuji?

133
00:17:48,810 --> 00:17:53,620
In the past ten years, Plough and Megrez have only communicated through letters.

134
00:17:53,620 --> 00:17:56,800
There is no war now and we didn't invite him.

135
00:17:56,800 --> 00:17:58,630
Why would he personally come?

136
00:17:58,630 --> 00:18:02,990
The messenger said that he's here to especially visit Her Majesty.

137
00:18:02,990 --> 00:18:06,890
And he brought the medical sage Zong Yue to look at the Queen.

138
00:18:06,890 --> 00:18:07,890
Really?

139
00:18:07,890 --> 00:18:10,580
Your Highness, I also have a secret message.

140
00:18:10,580 --> 00:18:14,600
Crown Prince Wuji said that you must personally open it.

141
00:18:27,860 --> 00:18:29,650
Your Highness.

142
00:18:35,700 --> 00:18:39,240
We seemed to have met Crown Prince Wuji on the streets the other day.

143
00:18:39,240 --> 00:18:42,570
That fair-skinned scholar that you mistakenly tried to arrest is the Medical Sage Zong Yue.

144
00:18:42,570 --> 00:18:45,860
And his helper is Crown Prince Wuji.

145
00:18:45,860 --> 00:18:49,690
Could it be that they are coming here to seek justice?

146
00:18:49,690 --> 00:18:51,480
You now know to be nervous?

147
00:18:51,480 --> 00:18:55,160
When I told you to arrest people before, didn't you know to open your eyes better?

148
00:18:55,160 --> 00:18:58,620
Can the people of Crown Prince Wuji even look like a minter?

149
00:18:58,620 --> 00:18:59,950
I didn't use my eyes well!

150
00:18:59,950 --> 00:19:01,940
Your Highness can punish me!

151
00:19:06,790 --> 00:19:10,170
How come I still find this matter fishy?

152
00:19:10,170 --> 00:19:14,790
Could it be that they have heard of some rumors?

153
00:19:16,850 --> 00:19:19,260
Could it be...

154
00:19:19,260 --> 00:19:21,610
the incident in Young Phoenix Lake!

155
00:19:24,770 --> 00:19:28,420
Since things have come to this, we can only take things one step at a time.

156
00:19:28,420 --> 00:19:29,670
Spread my order.

157
00:19:29,670 --> 00:19:31,230
He is after all the Crown Prince.

158
00:19:31,230 --> 00:19:37,690
He should be given the proper etiquette and respect.

159
00:19:37,690 --> 00:19:39,080
But at the same time,

160
00:19:39,080 --> 00:19:43,390
things that should be kept secret mustn't be leaked at all.

161
00:19:43,390 --> 00:19:45,170
Yes.

162
00:19:46,550 --> 00:19:50,480
Okay then. I'll take them to meet Queen Mother now.

163
00:19:50,480 --> 00:19:55,980
I want to see what tricks those two are plotting.

164
00:20:13,190 --> 00:20:14,860
Informing Your Highness,

165
00:20:14,860 --> 00:20:17,230
Her Majesty has become weaker today.

166
00:20:17,230 --> 00:20:20,210
She wouldn't even take her medicine now.

167
00:20:24,320 --> 00:20:25,820
Who was here earlier?

168
00:20:25,820 --> 00:20:29,520
It's... Second Queen Heir was here.

169
00:20:30,990 --> 00:20:34,390
Didn't I say that she isn't allowed to go anywhere without my order?

170
00:20:34,390 --> 00:20:36,540
Especially, she's not allowed to get near Astute Time Palace.

171
00:20:36,540 --> 00:20:38,080
How dare you!

172
00:20:38,080 --> 00:20:39,440
You even let her in?

173
00:20:39,440 --> 00:20:42,030
I think you don't want to live anymore.

174
00:20:42,450 --> 00:20:45,650
It's me who asked her to come.

175
00:20:46,950 --> 00:20:49,760
Is Medical Sage here?

176
00:20:49,760 --> 00:20:52,160
Crown Prince Wuij is also here.

177
00:21:19,060 --> 00:21:21,320
Your Highness Crown Prince has come here to Plough.

178
00:21:21,320 --> 00:21:24,130
I should have gone out to welcome you.

179
00:21:24,130 --> 00:21:28,520
However, I am currently severely ill and am looking quite haggard.

180
00:21:28,520 --> 00:21:31,420
I really couldn't get up and move around.

181
00:21:31,420 --> 00:21:34,960
Hope Your Highness Crown Prince can understand.

182
00:21:34,960 --> 00:21:37,630
Your Majesty, I came uninvited.

183
00:21:37,630 --> 00:21:39,380
Sorry to worry you.

184
00:21:39,380 --> 00:21:46,510
Right now, all the state affairs of my nation are being managed by my first queen heir, Feng Jingzhi.

185
00:21:46,510 --> 00:21:52,080
If you have any instructions, just order her to do it.

186
00:21:52,080 --> 00:21:54,220
Zhi'er.

187
00:21:55,700 --> 00:21:57,080
I'm here.

188
00:21:57,080 --> 00:22:01,120
His Highness Crown Prince is the most precious guest of our Plough.

189
00:22:01,120 --> 00:22:04,070
You must entertain him with the highest level of etiquette.

190
00:22:04,070 --> 00:22:06,300
There mustn't be any negligence.

191
00:22:06,300 --> 00:22:08,460
Queen Mother, don't worry.

192
00:22:09,770 --> 00:22:11,540
Thank you, Your Majesty, for treating me with utmost cordiality.

193
00:22:11,540 --> 00:22:15,510
Since this is the case, I'll then leave Zong Yue here to focus on curing you.

194
00:22:15,510 --> 00:22:17,720
I'll take my leave first.

195
00:22:34,980 --> 00:22:37,820
Why didn't you kneel when you saw me?

196
00:22:39,430 --> 00:22:42,310
Your Majesty, I'm not from Plough,

197
00:22:42,310 --> 00:22:44,310
but a guest that you invited.

198
00:22:44,310 --> 00:22:49,240
I never heard of any rule in Five Regions where a guest is asked to kneel.

199
00:22:50,310 --> 00:22:52,550
Come forward.

200
00:23:03,500 --> 00:23:07,860
The palace already prepared a lodging for you and Mister Zong.

201
00:23:07,860 --> 00:23:11,250
But because the inner palace is mostly made up of women,

202
00:23:11,250 --> 00:23:16,100
letting Your Highness and Mister stay here might be a bit inconvenient;

203
00:23:16,100 --> 00:23:20,790
hence, we especially emptied a palace hall in the east for you two.

204
00:23:20,790 --> 00:23:25,630
We've renovated it, but it's a bit far.

205
00:23:25,630 --> 00:23:29,490
Hope Your Highness Crown Prince won't mind it.

206
00:23:29,490 --> 00:23:31,770
Thank you.

207
00:23:31,770 --> 00:23:37,310
May I ask if the second queen heir you've mentioned is Folian who once had an engagement with me?

208
00:23:38,490 --> 00:23:43,020
She didn't want to be called the second queen heir and insisted on being called a princess.

209
00:23:43,020 --> 00:23:49,080
Isn't it announcing to the world that she doesn't want to be an heir and is rushing to be married off?

210
00:23:49,080 --> 00:23:55,710
Good thing, Crown Prince has sharp eyes. One look, and you discovered that Folian wasn't that easy to deal with.

211
00:23:55,710 --> 00:24:02,590
Your breaking the engagement early on is a extremely great thing for you and the Megrez Imperial City.

212
00:24:02,590 --> 00:24:05,700
Looks like your sibling relationship... ?

213
00:24:06,830 --> 00:24:11,510
If not because I considered the opinion of other people, she would have died long ago.

214
00:24:11,510 --> 00:24:14,720
That girl was harboring evil intentions since we were little.

215
00:24:14,720 --> 00:24:17,100
Letting her stay alive would just bring trouble to everyone.

216
00:24:17,100 --> 00:24:23,900
Now that she lost a backer like Megrez, she's worth nothing.

217
00:24:26,670 --> 00:24:31,620
Which means that once you inherit the royal throne, Folian will surely die.

218
00:24:32,050 --> 00:24:36,710
Your Highness Crown Prince, are you feeling pity towards her?

219
00:24:36,710 --> 00:24:39,070
Feeling pity?

220
00:24:40,970 --> 00:24:45,280
Why do you think she was rushing to marry you?

221
00:24:45,280 --> 00:24:47,280
She likes you.

222
00:24:47,280 --> 00:24:51,280
Someone that she met only once, more than ten years ago, she already like him?

223
00:24:51,860 --> 00:24:54,250
I don't believe it.

224
00:24:54,840 --> 00:24:57,000
There is a rule here in Plough royal clan.

225
00:24:57,000 --> 00:24:58,950
Once the new queen ascends to the throne,

226
00:24:58,950 --> 00:25:05,190
all her unmarried biological sisters must be executed to ensure a stable hold on the royal power.

227
00:25:05,190 --> 00:25:07,310
Folian was rushing to marry you.

228
00:25:07,310 --> 00:25:09,180
One: it's because she wants to be married off.

229
00:25:09,180 --> 00:25:13,730
Two: it's for your Megrez crown prince position.

230
00:25:13,730 --> 00:25:16,600
Who doesn't know that girl as being proud and arrogant?

231
00:25:16,600 --> 00:25:19,230
Always wanting to get on top of me.

232
00:25:19,230 --> 00:25:22,990
Don't you understand such kind of reasoning?

233
00:25:23,690 --> 00:25:25,570
I don't.

234
00:25:25,570 --> 00:25:27,830
I don't believe you.

235
00:25:28,790 --> 00:25:31,790
But all these are not important anymore.

236
00:25:31,790 --> 00:25:34,210
I have another idea.

237
00:25:35,280 --> 00:25:39,840
In the marital alliance between Megrez and Plough, Folian wasn't the only choice.

238
00:25:39,840 --> 00:25:44,960
I can also be a candidate, can I not?

239
00:25:44,960 --> 00:25:51,930
You promised to have an engagement with Folian before just to strengthen the alliance between Megrez and Plough.

240
00:25:51,930 --> 00:25:57,580
Based on that, am I, the First Queen Heir, not more suitable?

241
00:25:57,580 --> 00:26:03,090
If you say that you didn't have any such thoughts on rushing to Plough at this time,

242
00:26:03,090 --> 00:26:05,070
I still don't believe you.

243
00:26:05,070 --> 00:26:07,500
They all say that the first queen heir is very intelligent.

244
00:26:07,500 --> 00:26:10,310
I've seen it with my own eyes today.

245
00:26:10,310 --> 00:26:13,340
Give me time to think about it.

246
00:26:14,790 --> 00:26:21,910
There are a lot of royalty and nobility coming to my nation to ask for my hand in marriage.

247
00:26:21,910 --> 00:26:25,180
Don't miss out on the opportunity.

248
00:26:44,490 --> 00:26:49,260
Mistress, the person who is picking up the scriptures has arrived.

249
00:26:58,650 --> 00:27:01,280
This is the scripture that I've just copied today.

250
00:27:01,280 --> 00:27:03,850
Take it to the temple and offer it to the altar.

251
00:27:03,850 --> 00:27:08,410
Hope it can earn Queen Mother some blessings.

252
00:27:09,820 --> 00:27:11,620
Wait!

253
00:27:19,780 --> 00:27:26,760
The order, direction, and sequence of these scriptures require great attention.

254
00:27:26,760 --> 00:27:31,000
I think you won't know how to place them.

255
00:27:31,000 --> 00:27:33,550
It's better that I personally go.

256
00:27:34,880 --> 00:27:37,230
What are you doing?

257
00:27:37,230 --> 00:27:43,430
Mistress, Servant A'Mei was ordered to be flogged to death first thing this morning by First Queen Heir for letting you leave the palace.

258
00:27:43,430 --> 00:27:47,620
