262
00:27:57,410 --> 00:28:00,330
I was able to do a good deed.

263
00:28:00,330 --> 00:28:02,650
I beg you, Princess, leave me a chance to survive.

264
00:28:02,650 --> 00:28:04,280
I don't want to die!

265
00:28:04,280 --> 00:28:06,290
You're begging me.

266
00:28:06,290 --> 00:28:11,040
How can I then bare to see you suffer?

267
00:28:11,040 --> 00:28:16,030
Since you won't let me out,

268
00:28:16,030 --> 00:28:18,700
