373
00:38:09,990 --> 00:38:13,360
A black-clothed man with marks of Firmament.

374
00:38:13,360 --> 00:38:16,320
A Feng Xuan showing signs of being poisoned.

375
00:38:16,320 --> 00:38:19,060
A Young Phoenix Lake that's slowly drying up.

376
00:38:19,060 --> 00:38:22,420
I fear that Plough is indeed in trouble.

377
00:38:34,630 --> 00:38:37,900
